   319→  // punctuation token (/, &, +, :, or parenthesis), prefer the longer 2-line join as the
   320→  // complete heading. E.g. "SAFFRON WHEAT BUNS WITH QUARK" + "/ COTTAGE CHEESE (VARIATION D)".
